<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.1.9">
<l>pataka mutalaivāyp paṭṭa kaḷiṟu</l>
<l>kataṟikkai kūppiyeṉkaṇ ṇākaṇṇā veṉṉa</l>
<l>vutavappuḷ ḷūrntaṅ kuṟutuyar tīrtta</l>
<l>vatakaṉvan tappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟā</l>
<l rend="indent">ṉammaṉē yappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The strong one who, riding a bird in order to assist</l>
<l>the elephant who was caught in the mouth of the sinful crocodile,</l>
<l rend="indent">crying aloud in pain and lifting [its] trunk in worship</l>
<l rend="indent">while saying “my Kṛṣṇa! Kṛṣṇa!,”</l>
<l>ended the affliction that was experienced there,</l>
<l>he came and is making [the face of] a hobgoblin.</l>
<l>Oh! He is making [the face of] a hobgoblin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
